title: Stunning new 2 bedroom, 2bath apartment in Atlanta
posting_body: ['250sqft large room with a walk-in closet available for rent in Atlanta.', 'You would have access to a shared kitchen, laundry, dining, living and sunroom.', 'Off street parking with built-in basketball hoop.', 'The house sits on a ⅓ acre of land.', 'The ideal tenant would be mid 20’s to early 30’s, professional, clean, laid back person.', 'The room is $849 + ¼ utilities (water, gas, electric).', 'Ultra high speed internet, netflix, and Amazon Prime included.', 'Available NOW!', 'ok', 'Pets No Smoking.', 'An unfinished basement with abundant storage.', 'A driveway with space for two cars.', 'And a bonus shed in the back yard that can be used as an office or for additional storage.', 'Freshly painted and new roof just installed.', 'Dogs allowed.', 'If you interested please contact me :- kristi51523@𝐆𝐦𝐚𝐢𝐥com']
